tool_description:
Real-time data, unofficial airbnb API, get airbnb listings data, place to stay at an amazing price.

Airbnb com is a well-known and widely used online marketplace for short-term accommodation rentals around the world.

api_list.name: Get Languages
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://airbnb-search.p.rapidapi.com/languages"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "airbnb-search.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
